Write Code First EF layer which creates schema and populates master data (if any)
API Design on swagger
Get Product Details
Add Product
Get Product Price
Get Product Availability
Get Customer Details
Add product (qty) to cart
Place an order

Write implementation of 1 Get and 1 Post method so that we can test it from Postman